---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <section id="hero" class="relative mb-16 text-center overflow-hidden">
    <div id="tsparticles" class="absolute inset-0 z-0"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent/40 via-accent/20 to-accent/40 blur-3xl animate-gradient"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-10 left-1/4 w-40 h-40 bg-accent/20 rounded-full animate-float delay-[0ms] parallax-shape" data-speed="30"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-1/4 w-56 h-56 bg-accent/30 rounded-full animate-float delay-[2000ms] parallax-shape" data-speed="-20"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/10 rounded-full animate-float delay-[4000ms] parallax-shape" data-speed="45"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 px-4 py-20 animate-slideInUp">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent/80 via-accent to-accent/80 bg-[length:200%] bg-clip-text text-transparent animate-gradientText">
        Redefining Offensive Security
      </h2>
      <p class="text-subtext max-w-xl mx-auto">
        We help organizations identify, understand, and eliminate risk through deep technical expertise and real-world adversary simulation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="mb-16 reveal opacity-0" data-animation="slideInUp">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">About DarkVectr</h3>
    <p class="text-subtext">
      Darkvectr (spelled "Dark Vector") is an independent cybersecurity consultancy specializing in offensive security operations, red teaming, DevSecOps and secure architecture reviews. Founded by seasoned hackers with real-world breach experience, we provide deeply technical assessments designed to mirror modern threats.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="services" class="mb-16 reveal opacity-0" data-animation="slideInUp">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Services</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div data-tilt
        class="p-6 bg-surface rounded-lg shadow-lg group hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out reveal opacity-0"
        data-animation="slideInUp"
      >
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
          Red Team Engagements
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div data-tilt
        class="p-6 bg-surface rounded-lg shadow-lg group hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out reveal opacity-0"
        data-animation="slideInUp"
      >
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
          Penetration Testing (Web, API, Infra, Mobile)
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div data-tilt
        class="p-6 bg-surface rounded-lg shadow-lg group hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out reveal opacity-0"
        data-animation="slideInUp"
      >
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
          Threat Modeling & Secure Architecture
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div data-tilt
        class="p-6 bg-surface rounded-lg shadow-lg group hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out reveal opacity-0"
        data-animation="slideInUp"
      >
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
          Secure System Development Lifecycle
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div data-tilt
        class="p-6 bg-surface rounded-lg shadow-lg group hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out reveal opacity-0"
        data-animation="slideInUp"
      >
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
          Cloud Security Assessments
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div data-tilt
        class="p-6 bg-surface rounded-lg shadow-lg group hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out reveal opacity-0"
        data-animation="slideInUp"
      >
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
          AI Security Assessments
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div data-tilt
        class="p-6 bg-surface rounded-lg shadow-lg group hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out reveal opacity-0"
        data-animation="slideInUp"
      >
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
          Threat-Led Penetration Testing
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div data-tilt
        class="p-6 bg-surface rounded-lg shadow-lg group hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out reveal opacity-0"
        data-animation="slideInUp"
      >
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
          Security Advisory
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div data-tilt
        class="p-6 bg-surface rounded-lg shadow-lg group hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out reveal opacity-0"
        data-animation="slideInUp"
      >
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
          Security Training
        </h4>
      </div>
      <div data-tilt
        class="p-6 bg-surface rounded-lg shadow-lg group hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out reveal opacity-0"
        data-animation="slideInUp"
      >
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
          Virtual CISO
        </h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="approach" class="mb-16 reveal opacity-0" data-animation="slideInUp">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Our Approach</h3>
    <p class="text-subtext">
      With over 12 years of hands-on experience in the cybersecurity domain, we've held diverse roles spanning from system administration and DevSecOps to offensive security and red teaming. We've partnered with a broad spectrum of organizations: from agile startups to large multinational enterprises, gaining a holistic understanding of technologies, business processes, and the human factors that underpin them.
    </p>
    <p class="text-subtext mt-4">
      Our approach to security is fundamentally attacker-centric. Years of offensive experience have reinforced a core belief: the most effective way to defend is to deeply understand how attackers operate. This mindset, combined with custom tooling and real-world insights, allows us to deliver threat-informed, tailored, and high-impact security assessments that go far beyond checkbox compliance.
    </p>  
  </section>

    <section id="opensource" class="mb-16 reveal opacity-0" data-animation="slideInUp">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Open Source</h3>
      <p class="text-subtext mb-4">
        In the cybersecurity world, community and open source have given us so much: knowledge, tools, collaboration. Thatâ€™s why we believe in giving back.
      </p>
      <p class="text-subtext mb-4">
        We are active open source contributors, involved in various Special Interest Groups (SIGs) from organizations like <strong>OWASP</strong> and the <strong>Open Source Security Foundation (OpenSSF)</strong>. 
      </p>
      <p class="text-subtext mb-4">
        We're also the creators and maintainers of popular open source projects such as:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-subtext">
        <li><a href="https://github.com/R3DRUN3/sploitcraft/" class="text-accent underline" target="_blank">sploitcraft</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/R3DRUN3/vermilion" class="text-accent underline" target="_blank">vermilion</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>


  <section id="contact" class="mb-16 text-center reveal opacity-0" data-animation="slideInUp">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Ready to Test Your Defenses?</h3>
    <p class="text-subtext mb-4">
      Book a free discovery call or reach out securely.
    </p>
    <a
      href="mailto:hello@darkvectr.io"
      class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-accent text-background font-medium rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200 ease-in-out animate-pulse"
    >
      Contact Us
    </a>
  </section>
